snippet.title: Sonic CD: Miracle Edition (Full Playthrough)
snippet.description:
This video shows off my full playthrough of Sonic CD: Miracle Edition. This version of Sonic CD brings a lot of quality of life features and a new super form when you collect the Time Stones.
Sonic CD 2011 gameplay captured on PC.
#sonicthehedgehog #sonic #sonicfrontiers

‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒

✦ Sonic CD: Miracle Edition Mod by @peter4432
(peter4432's Gamebanana Member Page)
- https://gamebanana.com/members/1789065
(Mod Release Page)
- https://gamebanana.com/mods/467930
✦ MegAmi's Additions Mod by @MegAmi
(MegAmi's Gamebanana Member Page)
- https://gamebanana.com/members/1487155
(Mod Release Page)
- https://gamebanana.com/mods/50093
✦ Shields+ Mod by @Leonx254
(Leonx254's Gamebanana Member Page)
- https://gamebanana.com/members/1632841
(Mod Release Page)
- https://gamebanana.com/mods/50077

✦ Sonic CD 2011 Decompilation by Rubberduckycooly
- https://github.com/Rubberduckycooly/Sonic-CD-11-Decompilation
- https://github.com/Rubberduckycooly/Sonic-CD-2011-Script-Decompilation
